  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Many Township Early Childhood teachers are under-educated themselves. They are hungry for opportunities to increase their skills and provide a better learning experience for the children in their care. A generous donor sponsored Love to Langa&apos;s first Reporting Workshop for teachers on January 30, 2014 and it was a tremendous success. The 20 women who attended raved about the experience and are clamoring for more. With a waiting list for future workshops, we need funding to make them happen.</narrative>
  </description>
